@startuml presence-state

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName "Microsoft YaHei"
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #E0F2FE
  BorderColor #3B82F6
  FontColor #1E293B
  ArrowColor #3B82F6
  ArrowFontColor #64748B
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #FEF3C7
  BorderColor #F59E0B
  FontColor #1E293B
}

title LingoBridge 直播课堂 Presence 状态图

[*] --> 未创建

state "未创建" as NotCreated #F1F5F9 {
}

state "已计划\n(Scheduled)" as Scheduled #E0F2FE {
}

state "等待中\n(Waiting)" as Waiting #FEF3C7 {
}

state "进行中\n(Ongoing)" as Ongoing #D1FAE5 {
  state "正常听课" as Listening
  state "举手申请\n(HandRaised)" as HandRaised #FEF3C7
  state "已授权连麦\n(Authorized)" as Authorized #10B981

  [*] --> Listening

  Listening --> HandRaised : 学生点击举手按钮\n[role=student]
  HandRaised --> Listening : 学生取消举手\n/ 教师拒绝
  HandRaised --> Authorized : 教师批准连麦\n/ 触发 getUserMedia()
  Authorized --> Listening : 教师收回权限\n/ track.stop()
  Authorized --> Listening : 学生主动关闭连麦\n/ track.stop()
}

state "已结束\n(Closed)" as Closed #FEE2E2 {
}

NotCreated --> Scheduled : 教师创建直播课\n设定开始时间

Scheduled --> Waiting : 到达预定时间 -5min\n或教师手动打开等候室

Waiting --> Ongoing : 教师点击 "开始上课"\n/ 初始化 Presence 频道

Ongoing --> Closed : 教师点击 "结束课堂"\n/ 广播结束事件

Waiting --> Closed : 超时未开始\n(T > 30min)\n/ 自动关闭

Closed --> [*]

note right of Ongoing
  **媒体轨道生命周期:**
  1. 进入连麦 → navigator.mediaDevices.getUserMedia()
  2. 获取 MediaStream (camera/mic)
  3. 退出连麦 → stream.getTracks().forEach(t => t.stop())
  4. 断开连接 → 自动清理所有轨道
end note

note left of Waiting
  **Presence 心跳机制:**
  每 15s 发送心跳
  3 次未响应标记为离线
  重连后自动恢复状态
end note

note bottom of Closed
  **结束清理:**
  - 释放所有 MediaStream
  - 断开 Presence 连接
  - 更新 live_sessions.status = 'closed'
  - 记录 ended_at 时间戳
end note

@enduml
